    • Method Detail

      • createSqlClause

        java.lang.String createSqlClause​(java.sql.Connection connection,
                                 FunctionCompiler compiler)
        Creates a SQL clause for this instance. For TableSources it returns an identifier for the table usable in a FROM clause. For JdbcProjectionOperators it returns a list usable in a SELECT clause. For JdbcFilterOperators it creates a condition usable in a WHERE clause. For JdbcJoinOperator it returns a INNER JOIN statement usable in a JOIN clause. Also, these different clauses should be compatible for connected JdbcExecutionOperators.
        Parameters:
        compiler - used to create SQL code
        Returns:
        the SQL clause
